query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('es')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android-studio',
'angularjs',
'asp.net',
'bootstrap',
'c++',
'html5',
'json',
'laravel',
'laravel-5',
'python-3.x',
'sql-server')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Caucus',
'Critic',
'Notable Question',
'Peer Pressure',
'Yearling')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
